abstract: When a film is structured like a puzzle, qualities that are merely bewildering can be made to seem mysterious, if only for a while. Nicolas Roeg, who habitually structures his films this way, has again relied on jumbled time sequences, allusive cutting and a wealth of similar techniques to give "Bad Timing/A Sensual Obsession" its suggestive, secretive air.
headline_main: Film: Roeg 'Bad Timing' Starring Art Garfunkel; The Cast

abstract: "Murder is one of those things that could happen anywhere," Fred Harsh said the other day as he sat in his spacious sun-dappled backyard on South Elliott Place in the Fort Greene section of Brooklyn. But he was telling a visitor that what had happened was still a shock.

abstract: VIENNA, Sept. 16--Iran, Libya and  Algeria blocked an agreement today by  the Organization of Petroleum Exporting countries on a long-term strategy for pricing OPEC oil, creating a serious split in the ranks of the 13-member cartel.
